# Task 2 – Functional Scope

## Project
Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description
This task defines the functional scope of the Smart Library Request Workflow. It outlines the major system modules, including book management, borrow request management, workflow automation, role-based access control, and reporting.

## Functional Modules
- Book Management
- Borrow Request Management
- Workflow Automation
- Role-Based Access Control
- Reporting and Analytics

## Expected Outcome
A clear understanding of the system's functionality and feature boundaries before implementation.

## Technologies
- ServiceNow
- Flow Designer
- Access Control Lists (ACL)
- Workflow Management
- Reporting

## Status
Completed
